contribution-background-noise-description-extended = Ne nuЖ’oЖ’o si wolГ© Й–e mЙ”Мғ dzi la gblбәҪ, alo eЖ’e КӢuКӢudedi le КӢuКӢum la, gbe negbe Й–e woate ЕӢu ase nuЕӢЙ”ЕӢlЙ” bliboa kokoko hafi.
