contribution-background-voices-title = Gbe Siwo Le Megbe
contribution-background-voices-description = A quiet background hubub is OK, gake mГӯedi be gbe bubu siwo ate ЕӢu ana machine algorithm nade dzesi nya siwo mele nuЕӢЙ”ЕӢlЙ” si woЕӢlЙ” me o.вҖҷ Ne Г te ЕӢu ase nya siwo to vovo na nuЕӢЙ”ЕӢlЙ”a tЙ” la, ele be woagbe nya klipi la. Zi geЙ–e la, esia dzЙ”na le afisi wogblбәҪ TV la Й–o, alo afisi dzeЙ–oЙ–o aЙ–e le edzi yim le le teЖ’e si te Й–e eЕӢu.
contribution-background-voices-description-extended = Ne nuЖ’oЖ’o si wolГ© Й–e mЙ”Мғ dzi la gblбәҪ, alo eЖ’e КӢuКӢudedi le КӢuКӢum la, gbe negbe Й–e woate ЕӢu ase nuЕӢЙ”ЕӢlЙ” bliboa kokoko hafi.
